# Learning-based and classical methods Benchmark Logs

This repository contains experimental logs for the paper:

"A Benchmark Study of Deep Reinforcement Learning and Classical Control Methods for Autonomous Overtaking"

## Contents
- APF logs
- MPC logs
- DDPG logs
- SAC logs

## Description
The logs include performance metrics such as:
- Success rate
- Reward evolution
- Vehicle states
Due to GitHub file size constraints, only one representative log file per algorithm is included in this repository. These logs are intended to demonstrate the performance characteristics of each method. 
